Skills:
Requirements:
Software development experience (5+ years);
Advanced knowledge of Python 3+ / Python Core (language structures, standard libraries, regular expressions, etc.);
Experience with Django (Django ORM, Django Rest Framework (1+years);
Experience with AWS services: Lambda, API Gateway, SNS, SQS, SES, S3, RDS, VPC, EC2, CloudWatch, etc.
Experience writing API and working / integration with API of third-party services;
Knowledge of ​​the GraphQL API (Graphene will be a plus)
Knowledge of SQL (knowledge of PostgreSQL relational DBMS will be a plus)
Knowledge of CloudFormation in AWS and Terraform;
Ability to read code and understand it at the level of business logic;
Ability to work with general abstract tasks;
Written and spoken English is a MUST (B2+)

